Steps to get Things running:

1.) create your database (web.config sugests 'workplace') and do a aspnet_regsql.exe on it so the default authorisation stuff will work.
2.) add these roles with the configtool ( ~/asp.netwebadminfiles/security/roles/manageAllRoles.aspx )
		Administrator
		Manager
		TeamLeader
		Worker
3.) create a user account with the config tool ( ~/asp.netwebadminfiles/security/users/addUser.aspx )
4.) add the user to the Admin group.